Package: vitte-uninstall
Version: 2.1.2
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Vitte Team <maintainers@vitte.dev>
Depends: bash, coreutils, dpkg
Recommends: apt
Conflicts: vitte
Replaces: vitte
Description: Uninstaller package for Vitte toolchain
 This package removes Vitte binaries, runtime payload, shell wrappers,
 desktop launchers, icons, manpages and completion files.
